tified renovation firm and that the certified renovation firm must utilize a certified renovator to supervise each renovation and all other staff must be certified renovators or trained by a certified renovator. Makes changes in the provisions concerning licensing and administrative action.", "versions": [{"url": "http://ilga.gov/legislation/fulltext.asp?DocName=09700HB4969&GA=97&SessionId=84&DocTypeId=HB&LegID=64861&DocNum=4969&GAID=11&Session=&print=true", "doc_id": "ILD00052706", "name": "Introduced"}], "type": ["bill"], "id": "ILB00022764", "bill_id": "HB 4969"}